---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="demo-predictions" id="demo-predictions">
  <div class="container--wide">
    <h2 class="fade-up">Reason, Retrieve, and Predict with <span class="accent">LongNAP</span></h2>

    <div class="demo-predictions__hero fade-up">
      <div class="demo-predictions__hero-text">
        <p class="demo-predictions__intro">
          Rather than relying solely on parametric or in-context learning, we train models that <em>learn</em> to retrieve relevant past reasoning and observations into context. We instantiate this in LongNAP, a two-phase model trained end-to-end via policy gradients.
        </p>
        <p class="demo-predictions__intro">
          In the first phase, LongNAP <strong>reasons to retrieve</strong>: the model generates a chain-of-thought, then uses it to query a memory of past observations via BM25. In the second phase, LongNAP <strong>reasons to predict</strong>: integrating retrieved traces to refine its reasoning and predict concrete future actions. Traces that lead to good predictions are saved back into memory, so the library improves over time.
        </p>
        <p class="demo-predictions__intro">
          To score predictions, we use a <strong>temporal reward</strong>: since we can just wait and see what the user actually does, an LLM judge measures similarity between predicted and actual future actions. This lets us optimize both stages end-to-end through GRPO.
        </p>
        <div class="demo-predictions__results">
          <p class="demo-predictions__results-text">
            LongNAP significantly outperforms supervised finetuning (by <strong>79%</strong>) and prompted baselines (by <strong>39%</strong>). <strong>17.1%</strong> pass@1, rising to <strong>36.3%</strong> pass@20.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <figure class="demo-predictions__hero-figure">
        <img src={`${base}figures/fig2.jpg`} alt="LongNAP two-phase pipeline: reason-to-retrieve followed by reason-to-predict, optimized end-to-end with GRPO." loading="lazy" />

      </figure>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="container--full">
    <div class="predictions-grid" id="predictions-grid">
      <!-- Cards injected by JS -->
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-nav fade-up" id="carousel-nav">
      <button class="carousel-nav__btn" id="carousel-prev" aria-label="Previous card">&larr; Prev</button>
      <span class="carousel-nav__counter" id="carousel-counter">1 / 8</span>
      <button class="carousel-nav__btn" id="carousel-next" aria-label="Next card">Next &rarr;</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accent {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .demo-predictions {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .demo-predictions__intro {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .demo-predictions__hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 520px;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .demo-predictions__hero-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .demo-predictions__results {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.12), rgba(167, 193, 168, 0.12));
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .demo-predictions__results-text {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .demo-predictions__hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__body) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Carousel navigation */
  .carousel-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .carousel-nav__btn {
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .carousel-nav__btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .carousel-nav__btn:active {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .carousel-nav__counter {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    min-width: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Hide all cards by default; show only the active one */
  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card) {
    display: none;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card.active) {
    display: block;
  }

  .predictions-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card) {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card:hover) {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__header) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-tertiary);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__time) {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__utility) {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__body) {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7fr 3fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__screenshot) {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    background: var(--color-tertiary);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__columns) {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__col-label) {
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions) {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    scrollbar-width: auto;
    scrollbar-color: rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.4) rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.08);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions::-webkit-scrollbar) {
    width: 6px;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions::-webkit-scrollbar-track) {
    background: rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb) {
    background: rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.4);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions li) {
    padding: 2px var(--space-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions--predicted li) {
    background: rgba(129, 154, 145, 0.12);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__actions--true li) {
    background: rgba(238, 239, 224, 0.6);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-tertiary);
  }


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .predictions-grid :global(.pred-card__columns) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script src="../scripts/predictions.js"></script>
